	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Adding a modile channel</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Insert the Title. Leave the Location blank.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Insert the Maximun Channel size, Link Depth.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select Include Images (indicate the AvantGo server to grab images)</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select follow Offsite Links (check to indicate offsite links or otherwise)</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><i>NOTE: Most off-site links probably do not contain data optimized to be viewed on a handheld device. So leave the field unchecked.</i></td></tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select an option to indicate how often the channel will be refreshed.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Save button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><i>NOTE: Extra buttons appear after the channel is saved:</i></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Activate Channel</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Clicking on the Activate button creates and activates the channel in AvantGo.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Emulate Channel</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Clicking on the Emulate button pops-up a new window showing the content in the channel.</td></tr>
